 a new computer...help please:)</span><hr size=1> Ok I am building a new computer for a friend.  She has a few K to drop on it.  So im going balls to the wall on it.  The main thing I am hoping for is for someone to verify all the componants will match up.  Any help or advice is greatly appreciated.<br>
